<span id="freeTextContainer13891664375062887597">I just realized I hadn&apos;t rated this. Dur.<br/><br/>Oh, wow. Loved this book. Angel books are hard to do and this one is the best. And Kaidan? Can I lick him? Heck, I&apos;ll lick Wendy. Okay. Maybe shouldn&apos;t have written that. This is why I don&apos;t do reviews. Le sigh. </span>
  <span id="freeText13891664375062887597" style="display:none">I just realized I hadn't rated this. Dur.<br /><br />Oh, wow. Loved this book. Angel books are hard to do and this one is the best. And Kaidan? Can I lick him? Heck, I'll lick Wendy. Okay. Maybe shouldn't have written that. This is why I don't do reviews. Le sigh. </span>
