<span id="freeTextContainer14208354486975147123">This brilliant story had angels, demons, nephilims, and a big twisty prophecy that put me on the edge of my seat the whole time. Although the two main characters&apos; angsty love was very boring and tiring to read, but the book&apos;s rapid pace and suspenseful content kept me reading. As I came to the last page, I realized that I had really fallen in love with this first book of the series. </span>
  <span id="freeText14208354486975147123" style="display:none">This brilliant story had angels, demons, nephilims, and a big twisty prophecy that put me on the edge of my seat the whole time. Although the two main characters' angsty love was very boring and tiring to read, but the book's rapid pace and suspenseful content kept me reading. As I came to the last page, I realized that I had really fallen in love with this first book of the series. </span>
